<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Delivery | Express Line</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@500;600;700&family=Roboto:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    html{
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    html, body, div {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    h1, h2, span, p {
      font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      min-heigth: 700px;
      width: 100%;
      height: calc(100% - 32px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;

      background: #eee;

    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      color: #072ac8;
    }

    .container {
      width: 700px;
      height: 100%;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;

      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }

    .welcome, .thanks {
      padding: 32px 0 0 16px;
    }

    .welcome > p, .welcome > h2{
      font-size: 22px;
    }

    .thanks {
      color: #999;
    }

    .thanks > div > p, .thanks > div > h2 {
      font-size: 18px;

    }

    .thanks > div > h2, .welcome > h2{
      margin-left: 6px;
    }

    .welcome, .thanks > div {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .content {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .main-content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 32px;
    }

    .content > .main-content > p {
      margin: 0;
      margin-left: 4px;
    }

    .info-content {
      align-self: flex-start;
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .buttons {
      width: 100%;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
      padding-bottom: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;

      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }


    .buttons > a {
      min-width: 70%;
      height: 64px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;

      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;

      font: 600 20px Roboto, sans-serif;

      color: #fff;

      background-color: #072ac8;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <h1>Nova encomenda</h1>
      <div class="welcome">
        <p>Olá</p>
        <h2>{{deliverymanName}}</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="main-content">
        <p>Uma nova entrega foi destinada à você!</p>
        <p>O produto já está à sua espera!</p>
        <div class="info-content">

        <p>Produto: {{product}}</p>
        <p>Destinatário: {{recipientName}}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="buttons">
      <a href={{link}}>Verificar nova encomenda!</a>
    </div>

    <div class="thanks">
      <span>Obrigado pela sua atenção!</span>
      <div>
        <p>Atenciosamente, <p>
        <h2>Equipe Express Line</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
